## Step 3: Locked design decisions (do not re-open without PM)

These are **permanently locked** — do not ask about them again, do not propose alternatives:

| Decision | Locked value |
|---|---|
| Tone | Cozy/peaceful (Majesty-like) — never tense/battlefield |
| Ambient | Single neutral loop for Build A (`ambient_loop.wav`) |
| Variants | Build B only — Build A ships exactly one file per sound key |
| Audio is non-authoritative | Audio NEVER affects simulation state or determinism |
| Volume defaults | Master=0.8, Music=1.0, SFX=1.0 |
| Volume persistence | In-memory for Build A; file persistence deferred to Build B |
| Visibility gating | World SFX only if on-screen + `Visibility.VISIBLE`; UI sounds always audible |

